title: Klaus Doldinger - Passport
description:
PASSPORT is an German prog/rock/jazz/fusion band created by Ace Saxeman and Klaus Doldinger and formed in 1971.

For more info visit http://www.passportjazz.com

My favorities are Cross Collateral, Infinite Machine and Earthborn, but all of them are high quality material.

Really Worth the download.

I spent much time to compilate this, hope you enjoy it.

Eventually, torrent will be offline due to work on computer.
